						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of 90 sheep for burning a lamp in the temple of Tiruviśalūr-Perumāṇaḍigaḷ by one Kavisiyaṉ Mītuṇittañjaṉ of Talaichchaṅgāḍu. The <hi rend="italic">sabhā</hi> and the <hi rend="italic">Māhēśvaras</hi> were to protect this endowment.</p>						

						</summary>
